data.description: Beautiful 4 Bedroom/3 Bath Home on Oversized Greenbelt, Cul-De-Sac is Move-In Ready! Welcoming wood flooring leads to spacious family room with fireplace. Chef's Delight island kitchen offering granite counters, stainless built in appliances & 42" cabinets. Huge master retreat with walk in closet, double vanities & garden tub/separate shower. Secondary Bedroom down. Retreat to your own backyard sanctuary with private Greenbelt view & freshly stained fence. Water softener. No city taxes. Acclaimed Comal ISD.
